metadata.name: NFT Pioneers: Beeple
metadata.description: This NFT features Mike Winkelmann, also known as Beeple. He have been at the forefront in the NFT space and made worldwide headlines when an NFT he had created sold for $69,400,000 in March 2021. The NFT was created from a collage of images from his 'Everydays' series. This Hash Stamp is part of the series 'NFT Pioneers'. The original color version is completely unique and there is only 1 ever minted.
